title: Super Monkey Bananas v1.0
description:
Baby Monkey is hungry, so Mommy Monkey Chi-Chi set out to collect as many bananas as she could to fill Baby's tummy. Cute Baby Monkey has an enormous appetite for bananas and plantains, so Chi-Chi will have to work fast before time runs out and Baby is hungry again! Collecting bananas isn't easy for Mommy Chi-Chi however. Logging and Clear-Cutting of Monkey's Rain Forest has introduced many hazards for all of the jungle's cute baby animals. Watch out for falling logs while fetching your bananas. They don't make a hard hat in Mommy Chi-Chi's size! If you accidentally get hit, you will lose some of your bananas in the tumble.

Objective:

-Collect as many bananas as Baby Monkey demands
-Make sure you have enough bananas to feed Baby before time runs out
-Avoid being hit by tree logs
-Set a new record High Score, soon to be recorded online!

Bonuses:

-Collect bunches of bananas for triple (3x) the points

Controls:

-Use the on-screen coconut buttons
-Left arrow coconut goes left
-Right arrow coconut goes right
-Up arrow coconut makes monkey jump

Compatibility:

This video game should work fine on most modern phones and tablets running Android 2.3.3 and up. This game is also compatible with the newest Android v4.4 OS, KitKat. Performance will vary by device, with some running the game smoothly, while others somewhat choppy. I'm doing my best to resolve the performance issues on the slower devices, but a fix may take some time.
